{"tid":1525641,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請適當利用Fact Check","createTime":"2019-09-01T02:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T06:44:22.000Z","uid":11634,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1f9bdc226bc2525aaa0d113f7168c114be8842","tid":1525641,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:03:52.000Z","msg":"Fact Check的而且確係重要<br />\n但唔好再咁執著喺啲非必要嘅事<br />\n例如係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對運動有利嘅野</span><br />\n<br />\n睇返對家 你有冇曾幾何時見到佢地認抄車/柒咗<br />\n抄又點柒又點？自己知咪算囉<br />\n唔洗唱比全世界知你抄咗車嘅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對場運動有利嘅流料<br />\n自己人睇到咪唔好出聲 出面嘅人咪比佢地自己發酵囉</span><br />\n你FC完 佢地咪又話你放流料 堅料都話流架啦<br />\n唔通出嚟話你好有擔帶 識FC咩<br />\n<br />\n睇下個熱門 氣槍單野佔咗幾多<br />\n係比你發現咗抄車 咁又點<br />\n對我地好有利？定係知道咗就會贏？<br />\n<br />\n唔好再講咩我地同狗/藍絲係有分別 所以要咁做<br />\n你睇下琴日發生咗啲咩事先啦<br />\n到今時今日都仲要執著喺呢啲野度<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搶撚哂啲Focus呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TLDR</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">影響到自己人嘅野<br />\n=會造成恐慌/散水/行動上有影響 或 比大眾有唔好感觀嘅野<br />\n要FC</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">影響唔到<br />\n唔洗FC<br />\nFC咗都唔洗衝出嚟宣布</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"86326342c7f82cbca1bd1365aa3612f476ffce91","tid":1525641,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:04:50.000Z","msg":"啲三毛post就冷處理啦<br />\n負皮都冇撚用架 直接唔撚好推啦"},{"pid":"b9715e5458c0a7ed406c12617d5963b0a3e1dbf9","tid":1525641,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:05:41.000Z","msg":"係咁乜都FC 啲行動post 文宣post<br />\n沉撚哂架啦"},{"pid":"4c00b49c36497dd92875e0e2b9e647654ea1f51f","tid":1525641,"uid":307143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:06:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e734a57b329adcabf776cfdd3322ab1eeaa65e96","tid":1525641,"uid":11634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"